1	/**
2	 * FAM-01 — nested family resolver tests.
3	 *
4	 * Exercises:
5	 *   - 2-level nested family expansion with formula bindings
6	 *   - host_param + literal binding resolution
7	 *   - cycle detection (BFS) at save time
